[
  {
    "startTime": 0.209,
    "endTime": 5.3389999999999995,
    "text": "When SpongeBob sees plaid, he has this uncontrollable urge to cluck like a chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.176,
    "endTime": 10.4,
    "text": "Did somebody say plaid?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.6,
    "endTime": 12.387,
    "text": "Well, I'm a plaid enthusiast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.554,
    "endTime": 14.348,
    "text": "I just got me new kilt today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.932,
    "endTime": 17.1,
    "text": "Oh, SpongeBob. Can you come here, please?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.559,
    "endTime": 19.478,
    "text": "I couldn't find that watch anywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.77,
    "endTime": 21.104,
    "text": "All I found was this stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.188,
    "endTime": 22.230999999999998,
    "text": "I fell in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.314,
    "endTime": 23.232,
    "text": "And that guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.315,
    "endTime": 25.859,
    "text": "What do you think of Mr. Krabs' new plaid kilt?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.943,
    "endTime": 29.196,
    "text": "P-p-p-plaid?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.279,
    "endTime": 30.614,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.37,
    "endTime": 38.872,
    "text": "You don't have to be nasty about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.543,
    "endTime": 44.002,
    "text": "Avert your eyes, SquarePants."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.42,
    "endTime": 47.214,
    "text": "Can you explain the plan again, Squidward?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.297,
    "endTime": 49.090999999999994,
    "text": "Sure. But first, put on this cologne."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.133,
    "endTime": 51.051,
    "text": "Steaks sauce?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.97,
    "endTime": 56.598,
    "text": "Okay, so you two are dressed as Choice Cuts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.682,
    "endTime": 59.309000000000005,
    "text": "You go in there and yell, \"trick or treat\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.393,
    "endTime": 66.859,
    "text": "The worm will realize he forgot to stock up on Halloween candy, he'll leave to buy some, then we take the mattress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.859,
    "endTime": 68.151,
    "text": "Give me that cologne."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.069,
    "endTime": 70.61200000000001,
    "text": "Now get in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.779,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "Happy Halloween, Squidward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.126,
    "text": "Gum under all tables."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.251,
    "endTime": 86.628,
    "text": "How's that for low expectations?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.712,
    "endTime": 87.504,
    "text": "Lower!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.588,
    "endTime": 90.841,
    "text": "Initiating Stage 2: Collateral Damage!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.677,
    "endTime": 95.846,
    "text": "- How was that? - Perfect!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.929,
    "endTime": 97.09700000000001,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.181,
    "endTime": 103.478,
    "text": "If you burn out your laugh box, you'll live your whole life without ever laughing again!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.146,
    "endTime": 106.023,
    "text": "Hey, Patrick, you want to hear a joke?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.315,
    "endTime": 107.482,
    "text": "Sure, Sandy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.192,
    "endTime": 110.40199999999999,
    "text": "Sure. I'd love a good laugh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.986,
    "endTime": 113.906,
    "text": "What has four wheels and flies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.989,
    "endTime": 114.781,
    "text": "A garbage truck!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.834,
    "endTime": 128.25300000000001,
    "text": "I don't want to burn out my laugh box, Squidward!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.712,
    "endTime": 130.797,
    "text": "You know what he does next?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.881,
    "endTime": 134.051,
    "text": "- What? - You really want to know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.134,
    "endTime": 138.42999999999998,
    "text": "- What? - Are you sure you want to know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.514,
    "endTime": 140.55700000000002,
    "text": "What?! What?! What does he do?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.058,
    "endTime": 142.309,
    "text": "He gets ya!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.317,
    "endTime": 151.52700000000002,
    "text": "\"He gets ya!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.196,
    "endTime": 155.364,
    "text": "Oh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.409,
    "endTime": 162.24599999999998,
    "text": "Oh, Mr. Krabs! I'll listen, I promise!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.329,
    "endTime": 164.16400000000002,
    "text": "Whoa! Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.248,
    "endTime": 165.874,
    "text": "Please, save me, Mr. Krabs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.958,
    "endTime": 169.127,
    "text": "I promise I'll be good!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.878,
    "endTime": 170.838,
    "text": "Phew."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.507,
    "endTime": 175.592,
    "text": "Oh, look!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.553,
    "endTime": 179.304,
    "text": "It's SpongeBob NudiePants!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.183,
    "endTime": 185.519,
    "text": "Well, that was more SpongeBob than I needed to see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.811,
    "endTime": 188.68900000000002,
    "text": "Mr. Squidward, that was some fine angling!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.856,
    "endTime": 190.482,
    "text": "Do you think the lad has learned his lesson?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.566,
    "endTime": 193.94400000000002,
    "text": "Oh, I think he'll remember this for a long time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.319,
    "endTime": 200.367,
    "text": "The Flying Dutchman swoops down and starts stealing people's souls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.951,
    "endTime": 202.119,
    "text": "Do souls look like pickles?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.3,
    "endTime": 204.037,
    "text": "As a matter of fact, they do!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.204,
    "endTime": 206.62300000000002,
    "text": "Then he puts them where you can never get 'em..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.374,
    "endTime": 208.876,
    "text": "In his soul bag!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.67,
    "endTime": 213.797,
    "text": "I've come for your pickle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.716,
    "endTime": 219.011,
    "text": "Hah! ScaredyPants gets easier to scare every year!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.139,
    "endTime": 224.39100000000002,
    "text": "Ah! Look what you've done to me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.474,
    "endTime": 226.85199999999998,
    "text": "Oh! When I get my hair done you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.935,
    "endTime": 229.188,
    "text": "Please, Mr. Squidward's ghost!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.271,
    "endTime": 231.773,
    "text": "Spare us your ghostly anger!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.857,
    "endTime": 235.736,
    "text": "Oh, yes, Mr. Squidward's ghost! Please, don't haunt us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.819,
    "endTime": 237.613,
    "text": "We'll do anything you want!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.696,
    "endTime": 239.489,
    "text": "Just have mercy on us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.573,
    "endTime": 240.824,
    "text": "Enough!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.908,
    "endTime": 242.451,
    "text": "Listen up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.534,
    "endTime": 246.95499999999998,
    "text": "Squidward's ghost is feeling unusually generous today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.039,
    "endTime": 251.29299999999998,
    "text": "He has decided to spare ye a horrible fate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.22,
    "endTime": 263.889,
    "text": "Oh, boy! Something for me to clean up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.731,
    "endTime": 274.399,
    "text": "April Fools'!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.36,
    "endTime": 277.444,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.528,
    "endTime": 278.57,
    "text": "Hah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.654,
    "endTime": 279.738,
    "text": "Ha-hah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.407,
    "endTime": 284.159,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.749,
    "endTime": 292.37600000000003,
    "text": "Oh, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.474,
    "endTime": 308.59999999999997,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.268,
    "endTime": 311.186,
    "text": "I'll catch you, SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.361,
    "endTime": 320.445,
    "text": "Oops!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.078,
    "endTime": 330.789,
    "text": "April Fools'! You little sausage!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.172,
    "endTime": 340.29900000000004,
    "text": "SpongeBob! I was just kidding!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.716,
    "endTime": 344.386,
    "text": "Come on! Come on! You guys know I was just kidding!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.469,
    "endTime": 345.387,
    "text": "Right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.346,
    "endTime": 348.891,
    "text": "Oh, man. Poor kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.974,
    "endTime": 351.768,
    "text": "That guy has definitely got some issues to work out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.605,
    "endTime": 356.565,
    "text": "April Fools', jerk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.648,
    "endTime": 358.108,
    "text": "Wait, don't go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.067,
    "endTime": 361.028,
    "text": "Hey! You stink!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.111,
    "endTime": 363.864,
    "text": "Wait, wait! Wait, it was a joke!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.948,
    "endTime": 368.202,
    "text": "Must've been pretty good to make him cry like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.997,
    "endTime": 374.249,
    "text": "April Fools', jerk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.502,
    "endTime": 377.961,
    "text": "You stink!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.838,
    "endTime": 382.09000000000003,
    "text": "All right! All right! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.174,
    "endTime": 383.467,
    "text": "I admit it, I'm sorry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.55,
    "endTime": 387.05400000000003,
    "text": "I didn't mean to hurt you. In fact, SpongeBob, I like you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.137,
    "endTime": 388.472,
    "text": "I like living next door."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.555,
    "endTime": 392.601,
    "text": "I like hearing your foghorn alarm in the morning and your high-pitched giggling at night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.684,
    "endTime": 398.81500000000005,
    "text": "I also like Gary, Patrick, Sandy, Mr. Krabs, and all the other people I'm forced to be in contact with!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.692,
    "endTime": 404.363,
    "text": "- Squidward, is all that true? - Yes! Yes, SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.821,
    "endTime": 406.82300000000004,
    "text": "Yes, it's all true!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.407,
    "endTime": 409.409,
    "text": "Even the part about the Lima beans and the car chase?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.493,
    "endTime": 411.912,
    "text": "The what...? Yes, yes! Whatever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.995,
    "endTime": 413.747,
    "text": "But you have to promise not to tell anybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.83,
    "endTime": 415.49899999999997,
    "text": "- I promise. - Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.166,
    "endTime": 418.544,
    "text": "April Fools'!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.423,
    "endTime": 425.551,
    "text": "April Fools'! You're right, April Fools'!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.634,
    "endTime": 426.844,
    "text": "I just fooled you all!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.348,
    "endTime": 433.308,
    "text": "What would we do without Squidward?"
  }
]